<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
   <meta charset="UTF-8">
   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
   <title>Job Application</title>
   <style>
      body {
         font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
         line-height: 1.6;
         background-color: #f4f4f4;
         margin: 0;
         padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
         max-width: 600px;
         margin: 20px auto;
         padding: 20px;
         background: #fff;
         border-radius: 8px;
         box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      h1 {
         color: #333;
         text-align: center;
      }

      p {
         color: #555;
      }

      .signature {
         margin-top: 20px;
         font-style: italic;
         text-align: center;
      }
   </style>
</head>

<body>
   <div class="container">
      <h1>Job Application</h1>
      <p>Dear <%= recruiterName %>,</p>
      <p>I am writing to express my strong interest in the <%= postName %> position at <%= companyName %>.</p>
      <p>Please find attached my resume for your reference.</p>
      <p>Thank you,</p>
      <p class="signature">R.Sarangan</p>
   </div>
</body>

</html>